OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late brightness.
OL,7,FThen thickening cloud will bring rain
OL,8,Facross all parts for a time overnight.
OL,9,FRain turning light and patchy later on.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FOvernight rain soon clearing
OL,12,Fthen dry and cloudy during the
OL,13,Fmorning. Rain will spread northeast
OL,14,Facross all parts for a time during the
OL,15,Fafternoon then drier by evening. Warm.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry on
OL,18,FFriday morning but rain likely for a
OL,19,Ftime in the afternoon and evening.
OL,20,FDry, bright and warm over the weekend.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
